37521>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SetActionButtons
37524>>>>>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
37524>>>>>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
37524>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
37524>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDD
37524>>>>>>>>>
37524>>>>>>>>>        Get Server to hoDD
37525>>>>>>>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
37526>>>>>>>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
37527>>>>>>>>>
37527>>>>>>>>>        // let's hide all buttons and then Show the ones we want
37527>>>>>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to False
37528>>>>>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to False
37529>>>>>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to False
37530>>>>>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to False
37531>>>>>>>>>
37531>>>>>>>>>        If (NavigateData.bReadOnly) Begin
37533>>>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to True
37534>>>>>>>>>        End
37534>>>>>>>>>>
37534>>>>>>>>>        Else Begin
37535>>>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
37536>>>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
37537>>>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
37538>>>>>>>>>        End
37538>>>>>>>>>>
37538>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
