37549>>>>>>>>>
37549>>>>>>>>>    Procedure OnNavigateForward tWebNavigateData NavigateData Integer hoInvokingView Integer hoInvokingObject
37552>>>>>>>>>        Case Begin
37552>>>>>>>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromMain)
37554>>>>>>>>>                // If from main, this is a propbably a main file Select to Zoom.
37554>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
37555>>>>>>>>>
37555>>>>>>>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromParent)
37558>>>>>>>>>                // If from parent, this is a constrained drill down.
37558>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
37559>>>>>>>>>
37559>>>>>>>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromChild)
37562>>>>>>>>>                // If from child, this is a probably a parent Zoom from a Zoom.
37562>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
37563>>>>>>>>>
37563>>>>>>>>>            Case Else // must be nfUndefined
37563>>>>>>>>>
37563>>>>>>>>>        Case End
37563>>>>>>>>>
37563>>>>>>>>>        Send SetActionButtons
37564>>>>>>>>>
37564>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
37565>>>>>>>>>
37565>>>>>>>>>End_Object 
