37869>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
37869>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
37869>>>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
37869>>>>>        Handle hoDD
37869>>>>>
37869>>>>>        Get Server to hoDD
